name: Complete (Luak Games)
description:
Movement - W A S D

Complete is a game about getting to the other side of a relationship. It fits the theme of the geo jam because you have to get to the other side of the level (hence getting to the other side of the relationship)

[WARNING: THIS GAME WAS MADE IN UNDER 11 HOURS OF TIME OVER 3 DAYS] Please keep that in mind when playing!

NOTE: the way that web-gl is set up with itch.io makes it so that some parts of the level are cut out. If there are any problems with this please just download the game and extract the files. (this is for optimal gameplay)
